Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:28.06,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'd...}Mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:32.26,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{Oh, did you hear, Katase-san?}Chị có nghe không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:36.54,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{Yoshida-san from PR is getting reassigned.}Yoshida bên ban quảng cáo bị chuyển vị trí đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:39.29,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yoshida-san...?}Yoshida?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:43.80,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{He was apparently fooling around \Nwith Ito-san while on the clock.}Nghe nói âu yếm với Itou trong giờ làm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.19,0:13:46.60,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{There were a ton of witnesses, too.}Có rất nhiều người thấy nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:49.05,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{They were so into each other \Nthey probably didn't notice.}Họ âu yếm tới nỗi chẳng để ý ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:55.56,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I guess with office romances, \Nsomeone will need to get reassigned, huh?}Tình cảm công sở thì đành phải vậy thôi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:14:00.31,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{I dunno. I think this is mostly \Nabout it affecting their work.}Cũng chưa chắc, lần này em nghĩ \Nchủ yếu do ảnh hưởng đến công việc thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:06.36,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Reassignment...}Chuyển công tác...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:11.67,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{It's kind of a shock, though.}Nhưng cũng hơi sốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:18.08,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,700)\fs18\c&H0D0D0D&\bord4\shad0\b1\an2\3c&HFDFFFD&\pos(78.667,178.667)}{The way\Nthey were\Nbefore}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:15.88,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{I always thought those two \Nwere pretty cool and impressive.}Em từng nghĩ bọn họ rất ngầu và truyền cảm hứng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.32,Main - Top,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{All right, let's move on!}Rồi, tiếp tục thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:14.62,Main - Top,Ito,0,0,0,,{I've got it!}Cứ để tôi lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.06,Main - Top,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{I've got your back!}Yên tâm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:17.53,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{But then...}Vậy mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:21.59,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(725,700)\fs18\c&H0D0D0D&\bord4\shad0\b1\an2\3c&HFDFFFD&\pos(78.667,178.667)}{The way\Nthey are\Nnow}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:18.96,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Yuri-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:20.38,Main,Ito,0,0,0,,Masa-tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.59,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Yuri-tan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:25.09,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{That is }{\i1}{such}{\i0}{ a thing. Guys who\Nchange the second they get a girlfriend.}Có nhỉ. Những tên đàn ông \Nthay đổi 180 độ vì người yêu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.80,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{I know, right?}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.65,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Is it really so common?}Có luôn hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:32.72,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{Oh, totally! They try to act cool \Nin front of their friends...}Vâng! Họ hay ra vẻ ngầu lòi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:35.80,Main,Playboy Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{This? It's my chick.}Đây á? Gái của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:38.33,Main,Playboy Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Cute? I dunno. Isn't she average?}Dễ thương? Cũng bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:41.68,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{Or they try to white knight too hard.}Hoặc tỏ ra kiểu hiệp sĩ bảo vệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:44.54,Main,Playboy Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Isn't he staring at you too much?}Tên đó nhìn em hơi lâu đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:46.44,Main,Playboy Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Next time he looks, \NI think I'll let him have it.}Lần sau còn thế thì anh giết.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.59,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Funnily enough, it's the serious, \Ndown-to-earth types}Thật buồn cười khi kiểu người như vậy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:54.65,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{who tend to go haywire \Nwhen they get a girlfriend.}sẽ trở nên rắc rối hơn khi có bạn gái.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:58.50,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{And worst of all are the ones \Nwho go infantile once they start dating.}Tệ nhất là những tên trở nên trẻ con khi bắt đầu yêu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.64,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Infantile?}Trẻ con?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:03.75,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{I guess they want to be babied? \NThey want pats on the head and stuff.}Kiểu như muốn được làm nũng ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:09.29,Main,Googoo Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Shenpai! Sweepy! Gib headpats!}Chị ơi! Em mệt quá, xoa đầu đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:13.58,Main,Motherly Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, if you insist. Good boy.}Thôi nào, thiệt tình mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:15.76,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{C-Cute...}D-Dễ thương quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:19.04,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I-I think that might be kind of nice...}C-Chị nghĩ mình thích thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:20.56,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Isn't it cute?}Nó dễ thương mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:24.01,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, you've always \Nhad shotacon vibes, Katase-san.}Nghĩ lại thì chị thuộc shotacon mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:28.57,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm a... shota... shota... shota...}C-C-Chị là shota...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:36.33,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm a... shota...}Là shota...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:33.18,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{What's your type, Hayakawa-san?}Còn cậu thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:36.33,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{M-Me...?}T-Tớ á?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.57,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Someone who does good work, who's kind,}Ai đó... giỏi công việc, tốt bụng...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:40.67,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{has a good head on their shoulders \Nand is understanding of my hobbies,}thông minh và hiểu rõ sở thích của tớ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:42.67,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{and always looks out for me...}lúc nào cũng bảo vệ tớ nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:46.22,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{You're not gonna find a dreamboat like that \Nin reality. Come back down to Earth.}Cậu tìm kiếm hình mẫu trong anime à? Tỉnh táo lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:49.34,Main,Ito,0,0,0,,{What a fun topic.}Thú vị nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:52.33,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{Ito-san?}Itou?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:55.33,Main,Ito,0,0,0,,{It's true that women can make men change...}Đúng là phụ nữ có thể khiến đàn ông thay đổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:56.26,Main,Ito,0,0,0,,{But!}Nhưng!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.78,Main,Ito,0,0,0,,{Men can change women, too.}Đàn ông cũng khiến phụ nữ thay đổi nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:02.89,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Yuri-tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.11,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{So this is where you've been, Yuri-tan!}Em ở đây à, Yuri-tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.86,Main,Ito,0,0,0,,Masa-tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:11.31,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{I'm so sorry for leaving you alone like that!}Anh xin lỗi vì để em lại một mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:15.87,Main,Ito,0,0,0,,{It's okay! Absence makes the heart grow fonder.}Không sao! Càng ít gặp nhau tình cảm càng sâu đậm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:17.52,Main,Ito,0,0,0,,{Isn't that right?!}Phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:19.37,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{Yes, it certainly is!}Ừ, phải rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.37,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Yuri-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:23.37,Main,Ito,0,0,0,,Masa-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:27.28,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{Smoochie!}Chút!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.72,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{They've gone totally, completely...}Bọn họ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.88,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{...absolutely stupid.}...hoàn toàn là lũ ngốc...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:30.86,Main,Ito,0,0,0,,Masa-tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:33.07,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Yuri-tan, I'll never let you go again!}Yuri-tan, anh sẽ không rời xa em!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:34.57,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Totally, completely... absolutely stupid.}Đúng là cặp đôi ngu ngốc...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:35.89,Main,Ito,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Masa-tan, hold me tight!}Masa-tan, ôm em thật chặt đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:44.39,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That display in there \Nwas a little too spicy for me.}Cảnh vừa rồi có hơi... quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:49.06,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Is that what would happen?}Chuyện đó sẽ xảy ra sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.98,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Acting like that...}Chuyện như vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:56.09,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm so sorry I left you alone!}Xin lỗi vì đã để chị một mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:17:00.66,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's okay! Absence makes the heart grow fonder!}Không sao! Càng ít gặp nhau tình cảm càng sâu đậm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.30,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Isn't that right?}Phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:04.16,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah! You're right!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:06.17,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Shiorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.17,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Takkun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.17,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Squeeze!}Chút!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:14.01,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Totally, completely... absolutely stupid.}Hoàn toàn... ngu ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:24.36,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm finally gonna tell Senpai...}Cuối cùng mình cũng...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:30.36,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I can't run away! I need to brace myself!}Không thể bỏ chạy! Phải can đảm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:35.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san.}Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.41,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai.}Chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:44.41,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Let's always be good coworkers, okay?}Chúng ta hãy mãi là đồng nghiệp thân thiết nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:49.17,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Because I don't want to be totally, \Ncompletely, absolutely stupid.}Vì mình không muốn thành cặp đôi ngốc đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:53.20,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I think having a relationship \Nthat stays the same is wonderful.}Chị nghĩ mối quan hệ không thay đổi là tốt nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:57.58,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Because being totally, completely, \Nabsolutely stupid would be awful.}Vì mình không muốn thành cặp đôi ngốc đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:03.36,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sorry, I kind of talked over you there.}Xin lỗi, chị quên mất...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:06.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What did you want to discuss, Shinozaki-san?}Em muốn nói gì hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:10.90,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I...}Em...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.44,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I was going to say the same thing!}Em cũng muốn nói như vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:16.06,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That's great!}Vậy thì tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:18.45,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{We're on the same wavelength.}Chúng ta cùng tần số rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:21.19,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{We sure are.}Vâng ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:25.95,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I was really worried you were having \Ntrouble with work or something!}Chị cứ tưởng em gặp\N rắc rối gì trong công việc chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:28.46,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Are you going home now? \NLet's head to the station together.}Đi về cùng nhau thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:29.50,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah, sure.}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:47.17,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Bleary-eyed and not fully awake from a dream}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:52.07,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{I still can't bring myself \Nto drink that bitter coffee}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:56.55,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{So I sneakily toss in \Ntwo pinches of a sweet secret}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:19:00.77,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{And let it slowly spread throughout}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:05.73,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{There's a local bakery \Nthat's only open sometimes}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:10.62,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Where I once had some toast that glittered}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:15.12,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{What is it that makes it so satisfying?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:19.29,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Almost like magic}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:24.37,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{I find myself thinking about that kind of thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:29.98,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{How the small things can be the most precious}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:34.77,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Deep inside my heart}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:39.17,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{It's ever so bittersweet}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:44.09,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{"Just being around you is enough"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:48.11,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Becomes my mantra}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:50.40,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Baby like sugar}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.66,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Baby you're the sugar}
