Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:11.48,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{"Action! Shiorin"!}Xuất kích Shiorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:13.48,Main,Yutakappi,0,0,0,,{Big trouble, Shiorin!}Chúng ta rắc rối rồi Shiorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:15.48,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{What's wrong, Yutakappi?}Sao thế Yukatappi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:17.95,Main,Yutakappi,0,0,0,,{Bad guys are attacking! \NThe Demon Lord has come to town!}Lũ kẻ xấu đang tấn công! \NQuỷ vương sẽ đến thị trấn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:19.40,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{Is that true?!}Cái gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:20.97,Main,Yutakappi,0,0,0,,{Come on, Shiorin!}Đi thôi Shiorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:21.74,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:29.37,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{That's enough!}Đủ rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:33.36,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{Stop this right now, Demon Lord!}Dừng lại ngay Quỷ vương!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:35.58,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{Magical Girl Shiorin is here to face you!}Ma pháp thiếu nữ đã đến!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.09,Main,New Demon Lord,0,0,0,,{So, you've come, Magical Girl...}Ngươi đến rồi à...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:47.56,Main,New Demon Lord,0,0,0,,{I'm the new Demon Lord, \Nhere to take over for my predecessor.}Tôi là tân quỷ vương, người kế vị!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:50.10,Main,New Demon Lord,0,0,0,,{It's a pleasure to be working with you!}Rất vui được gặp mặt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.66,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,Xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:54.41,Main,New Demon Lord,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:57.65,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{All right, here goes!}Rồi, bắt đầu nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:06.09,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{I'm Magical Girl Shiorin.}Tôi là Ma pháp thiếu nữ Shiorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:08.46,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{It's a pleasure to make your acquaintance.}Mong cậu giúp đỡ!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:11.10,Main,New Demon Lord,0,0,0,,{Oh, let me accept your card.}À vâng, tôi xin nhận.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:15.63,Main,New Demon Lord,0,0,0,,{I'll probably need a while \Nto get used to everything, so...}Cho đến khi quen việc thì\N tôi xin lỗi vì đã làm phiền...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:19.90,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{It's only my third year doing this, so I know \Nthat everyone has to start somewhere.}Tôi cũng mới năm thứ 3 nên hiểu mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.43,Main,New Demon Lord,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:31.26,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{You can go ahead \Nand put the business card away.}Cậu có thể cất danh thiếp đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.27,Main,New Demon Lord,0,0,0,,{R-Right...}À vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:37.58,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{I know the timing can be kind of awkward.}Tôi biết lúc cất danh thiếp rất khó xử mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:39.40,Main,New Demon Lord,0,0,0,,{I appreciate your consideration.}Cảm ơn cô vì đã nhận ra...
