Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.79,Main,Haya Kawa,0,0,0,,{This is bad.}Tệ rồi đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:57.50,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{I'm so sorry, Professor Haya Kawa.}Xin lỗi tiến sĩ Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:21:59.88,Main,Yutakappi,0,0,0,,{You won't be able to transform now.}Giờ thì không thể biến hình được nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:02.99,Main,Haya Kawa,0,0,0,,{With your transformation \Ncompact in this state...}Nếu biến hình trong tình trạng này...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.99,0:22:06.17,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{I was running and it fell out of my bag.}Tôi đang chạy và nó rơi ra khỏi túi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:07.68,Main,Haya Kawa,0,0,0,,{Like a cell phone?!}Điện thoại hay gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:08.44,Main,Yutakappi,0,0,0,,{Da-ding!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:10.83,Main,Yutakappi,0,0,0,,{Enemy attack!}Địch tấn công!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:12.60,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{At a time like this?!}Vào lúc này sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:14.14,Main,Yutakappi,0,0,0,,{Come on, Shiorin!}Đi nào Shiorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:15.63,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:16.78,Main,Haya Kawa,0,0,0,,{We've got no choice.}Chịu thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:20.40,Main,Haya Kawa,0,0,0,,{It's older, but please, use it.}Dùng cái cũ này đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:22.44,Main,shiorin,0,0,0,,{Th-That is...}Đ-Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:25.85,Main,Haya Kawa,0,0,0,,{There's no other way right now!}Không còn cách nào khác đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:31.00,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{Stop right there!}Dừng lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.72,0:22:36.58,Main,New demon Lord,0,0,0,,{So, you've come, Magical Giiiirl—}Đến rồi à, ma pháp thiếu nữ--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:39.20,Main,New demon Lord,0,0,0,,{Wh-Wh-What happened to you?! What is that?!}C-C-Cái gì thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:41.21,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{There was a bit of an incident...}Có tai nạn xảy ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.21,0:22:43.71,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{so I'm using an older model \Nof transformation compact...}nên là tôi sử dụng mẫu cũ...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:45.78,Main,New Demon Lord,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The old days were hot!}Mẫu cũ phê vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:49.84,Main,New Demon Lord,0,0,0,,{Defeating you when you aren't \Nat your best would mean nothing.}Đánh bại cô trong tình \Ntrạng này cũng chả vẻ vang gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:51.72,Main,New Demon Lord,0,0,0,,{I'll take my leave, for today.}Hôm nay tôi về vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.72,0:22:53.35,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{Thank you so much.}Cảm ơn rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:55.53,Main,Shiorin,0,0,0,,{I'm so, so sorry...}Xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.53,0:22:59.03,Main,Former Demon Lord,0,0,0,,{I suppose this might be a job for me, \Nas the previous Demon Lord...}Đây là Quỷ vương kế nhiệm của ta à...
